name: To(o) Fall In
description: "To(o) Fall In" (2018) is an online art work created by Shay Benamram (bae4pay) and was presented as an interactive installation at the "New Artists' Gallery", Jerusalem. The work presented in the form of an interactive game, in which there is a capsule that simulates a journey within a virtual vacuum that has no definite boundaries, and like outer space, is supposed to be infinite
